au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.collections.tables

Interface MultiDimContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.DataContainer, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable

    public interface MultiDimContainer
extends fr.ens.biologie.generic.DataContainer, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable
    An interface for DataContainers indexd with Dimensioners, i.e. typically multi-dimensional tables of items of the same type. The size (dimensions) of such objects are set at construction time and immutable after.
    Author:
    gignoux
